messages.text: Had a great time last night.
It wasn’t too boring? Staying in?
You seemed kind of freaked out by the movie.
Because I’m pretty sure I heard you peek behind the shower curtain when you were in the bathroom.
You eavesdropped on me in the bathroom?
Actually, there’s something I need to tell you…
There’s something I need to tell you.
Where do you want to meet?
The park? The one where we had our first date :)
Hey! We’re still on for ten right? I got us a brunch reservation at Appertivo.
Yeah. Might be a few minutes late.
They don’t seat you until everyone’s arrived.
I’ll try to make it on time.
What could be more important than brunch?
Yes. Seeing as it’s my story. Our story. You know what I mean.
I’m sorry, Casey. I can’t do it.
This guy is a creep!! Remember?!?!
OMG! Are you falling for him?
Get ahold of yourself! It’s a game, remember?
What if it’s different this time?
That’s what he wants you to think.
I don’t know. It feels real.
I’m telling him, Casey. He’s a good guy.
Don’t make a decision like this on an empty stomach!
How did last night go? Give me the play by play.
Nothing. We had a great time.
So now you seal the deal, right? Break her heart.
Why do I sense a lack of conviction?
I don’t know, Graham. Maybe you’re projecting?
Sorry, my man. Can’t go through with it.
You can’t do this. We have a deal. I paid you.
Maybe I’m turning over a new leaf.
God. You’re supposed to be teflon.
Well, I guess every dog has his day.
You are supposed to break her heart.
I’m through with the burn game.
So it’s close to your apartment…
The park! Where you had your first date!
You’ll never get here in time.
I am so mad about my brunch reservation.
I need to talk to you.
Heard you have a new boyfriend.
Bet you think he’s something special.
Ever heard of the burn game?
So you know he’s running it on you, right?
If he is, it’s because my a-hole ex-boyfriend hired him to.
Touche. But I did it to help you.
So you’d get the story. You’re writing a story on him, right?
Because he’s running the game on someone else right now too.
I do because I had him followed.
It’s just a game Vera. You’re his next victim.
See the cab on the corner?
I should know. I hired him.
You have to believe me. I only did it to help you. To get you the story.
Hey. Thanks for letting me share the cab.
I know this has been hard. But it’s almost over.
I can’t believe he’s running the game on someone else at the same time.
I really felt like it was real.
Because he’s good at it. And if you could be fooled, think of those other women.
I’ll have the story to you tomorrow.
When do you want it to go live?
On our last date. I want to see him go down in person.
Sorry. My phone died and I was stuck on the bus. Did you wait long?
Yeah. I’ve never been stood up before.
Do you want to meet now?
How about our next date? We have so much to tell each other.
It’ll just make it more special :)
I just want to say thanks.
You always did push my career.
Maybe we should give it another try.
